[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    2842[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mReal API Gateway WebSocket plus Cognito authorizer for the app channel.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The demo handles only the telephony channel. Production fronts the app channel with API Gateway WebSocket API (audio frames flow over the WebSocket; intent results flow back) plus a REST API for session lifecycle. The Cognito authorizer validates the patient portal session token; the patient is identified by their portal-authenticated identity. The same Lex bot handles both telephony and app channels; the audio source and identity-context source differ at the edges.[K
